    Btrfs: get write access for scrub
    
    We need get write access for scrub, or we will modify the R/O fs.
    
    Signed-off-by: Miao Xie <miaox@cn.fujitsu.com>
    Signed-off-by: Chris Mason <chris.mason@fusionio.com>

